txt.en: In later days, the Black Blade of Lebennin was oft-seen stalking among the hills and forests of Western Gondor, striking fear into the hearts of Men with both deadly countenance and fearsome sword. For those few who did not flee, his words poured like honey into their unwilling ears and drove them to terrible acts of evil. This may have proved his worst and most effective weapon.
The Black Blade of Lebennin, defeated but enduring

In later days, the Black Blade of Lebennin was oft-seen stalking among the hills and forests of Western Gondor, striking fear into the hearts of Men with both deadly countenance and fearsome sword. For those few who did not flee, his words poured like honey into their unwilling ears and drove them to terrible acts of evil. This may have proved his worst and most effective weapon.

The Black Blade of Lebennin suffered defeat on the battlefield of Mordor Besieged, but it was not to be a lasting death... not while Sauron endured. The Nazg没l would return, for his was an existence beyond ending.

DNT - The Black Blade of Lebennin can be found patrolling Mordor Besieged.\n\nYou have encountered the Black Blade of Lebennin, one of the nine Nazg没l. The Black Blade of Lebennin commands many enemies upon the besieged planes of battle with might unmatched.
